{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-generic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/a1-professional-chinese/zh-a1-learn-nasal-finals/task-2","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"assignments":["<p>Slušao sam zvuk i vežbao izgovor nosa i slogova.</p>"],"bilibiliIds":null,"block":"zh-a1-learn-nasal-finals","challengeType":24,"description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Postoji 16 završetaka nosnih zvukova u Pinyinu. Ovo su slogovi koji se završavaju nosnim zvukom, bilo da je to <span class=\"highlighted-text\">n</span> (prednje nosno) ili <span class=\"highlighted-text\">ng</span> (zadnje nosno).</p>\n<p>Kraja nosa <span class=\"highlighted-text\">an</span> je prvi koji uči. Sastoji se od vokala <span class=\"highlighted-text\">a</span> zajedno sa krajem nosa.</p>\n<p>Da bi izgovorili <span class=\"highlighted-text\">an</span>, počnite sa kratkim vokalom <span class=\"highlighted-text\">a</span>, zatim malo zatvorite protok vazduha tako da jezik dodirne iza vaših gornjih zuba kako biste napravili zvuk <span class=\"highlighted-text\">n</span>. Važne usne treba da ostanu opuštene i blago otvorene. Ovo je završetak prednjeg nosnog zvuka zato što vrh jezika proizvodi nosni zvuk ispred usta.</p>\n<p>Kada <span class=\"highlighted-text\">an</span> je praćeno početnim konsonantima, može formirati slogove kao <span class=\"highlighted-text\">ban</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">pan</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">man</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">dan</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">lan</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">shan</span>, i <span class=\"highlighted-text\">ran</span>.</p>\n<p>Da bi izgovorio slog <span class=\"highlighted-text\">ban</span>, počnite sa zvukom početne konsonante <span class=\"highlighted-text\">b</span> spajanjem usana i polako puštanjem zvuka. Zatim odmah pređite na kraj <span class=\"highlighted-text\">an</span>.</p>\n<p>Ovaj sistem se koristi za sve slogove koji se završavaju sa <span class=\"highlighted-text\">an</span>. Jedina promena je početna konsonanta na početku sloga. Važno je lako povezati početni zvuk sa krajem <span class=\"highlighted-text\">an</span> bez pauze.</p>\n<p>Pokušajte izgovoriti <span class=\"highlighted-text\">an</span> po tim slogovima, a zatim koristite <span class=\"highlighted-text\">fan</span> u različitim tonovima kao primer.</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Pinyin</th>\n<th>Herufi</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">fān</span></td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">帆</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">fán</span></td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">烦</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">fǎn</span></td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">反</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">fàn</span></td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">饭</span></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</section>","nodules":null,"explanation":null,"helpCategory":"Chinese Curriculum","instructions":"","fields":{"slug":"/learn/a1-professional-chinese/zh-a1-learn-nasal-finals/task-2"},"questions":[],"scene":{"setup":{"background":"cafe.png","characters":[{"character":"Li Hong","position":{"x":50,"y":15,"z":1.4},"opacity":0}],"audio":{"filename":"ZH_A1_pinyin_nasal_finals.mp3","startTime":1,"startTimestamp":51.25,"finishTimestamp":75.35},"alwaysShowDialogue":null},"commands":[{"background":null,"character":"Li Hong","position":null,"opacity":1,"startTime":0,"finishTime":null,"dialogue":null},{"background":null,"character":"Li Hong","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":1,"finishTime":1.68,"dialogue":{"text":"an","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Li Hong","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":3.28,"finishTime":3.94,"dialogue":{"text":"ban","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Li Hong","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":5.27,"finishTime":5.96,"dialogue":{"text":"pan","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Li Hong","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":7.38,"finishTime":8.14,"dialogue":{"text":"man","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Li Hong","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":9.48,"finishTime":10.2,"dialogue":{"text":"dan","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Li Hong","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":11.53,"finishTime":12.25,"dialogue":{"text":"lan","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Li Hong","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":13.53,"finishTime":14.39,"dialogue":{"text":"shan","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Li Hong","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":15.64,"finishTime":16.44,"dialogue":{"text":"ran","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Li Hong","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":18.3,"finishTime":19.1,"dialogue":{"text":"fān","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Li Hong","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":20.22,"finishTime":21.15,"dialogue":{"text":"fán","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Li Hong","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":22.33,"finishTime":23.28,"dialogue":{"text":"fǎn","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Li Hong","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":24.52,"finishTime":25.1,"dialogue":{"text":"fàn","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Li Hong","position":null,"opacity":0,"startTime":25.6,"finishTime":null,"dialogue":null}]},"superBlock":"a1-professional-chinese","tests":[],"title":"Vežba 2","transcript":null,"translationPending":false,"videoId":null,"videoLocaleIds":null}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/a1-professional-chinese/#zh-a1-learn-nasal-finals","dashedName":"task-2","certification":"a1-professional-chinese","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"a1-professional-chinese","chapter":"zh-a1-chapter-pinyin","module":"zh-a1-module-initial